{
  "stem": "17299.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 292.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they brought the bodies back to the camp, and I had to pick-- pick all and throw the bodies in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had stones thrown on, and then buried.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was very abusive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And quite a few died on-- of starvation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then he cut off the water to the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The camp got filtered water before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he had dug a well in the camp, but the water was not clean, because it was not deep enough in the ground.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And a lot of diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], and more people died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then the SS commanding officer from the entire training camp for the SS start complaining.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He wanted to find out what was going on, that all of a sudden, the Jews were malnutrition and couldn't work anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they put another SS man in charge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then I found out what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then Blumenthal opened his mouth and said that Groscher was stealing [INAUDIBLE] and trading it in for alcohol with the Latvians-- especially sugar and things like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So Blumenthal got taken away [INAUDIBLE] later, and then he got shot for accusing an SS man of theft.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, anyway, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another commandant came on, which was even worse than Groscher in one way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was Gustav Zoger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He came order from Oranienburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oranienburg concentration camp, near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Zoger had the name, 'The Iron Gustav.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He would-- would be beating right and left, but he-- he put a new camp elder in, Werner Zamwel.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Werner Zamwel could convince him, said all Jews would be deloused.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That no more lice here on the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was-- he-- he finished that up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they had to work to make the campgrounds more livable.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
